# å˜èªï¼ˆç©ºç™½æ–‡å­—ã§åŒºåˆ‡ã‚‰ã‚Œã¦ã„ã‚‹ã‚‚ã®ï¼‰ã«å¯¾ã™ã‚‹è£œå®Œ
typeset -A word_abbrev
word_abbrev=(
	"tarc"	"tar czvf "
	"I"		"|"
	"L"		"| $PAGER "
	"G"		"| grep "
	"V"		"| vi -R - "
	"HD" "shigoro.dyndns.org"
	"SVH" "svn+ssh://"
)

# ãƒ‘ã‚¤ãƒ—ã«å¯¾ã™ã‚‹è£œå®Œ
typeset -A pipe_abbrev
pipe_abbrev=(
	"l"	"$PAGER"
	"g"	"grep"
	"s"	"sort"
	"w"	"wc"
	"h"	"head"
	"t"	"tail"
	"v" "vi -R -"
)

# å˜èªç•¥èªå±•é–‹
expand-word-abbrev()
{
	local left right abbrev
	# æœ€å¾Œã®å˜èª
	right=$(echo -nE "$LBUFFER" | sed -e 's/.*[[:space:]]\([^[:space:]]*\)$/\1/')
	abbrev=$word_abbrev[$right]
	
	if [ -z "$abbrev" ] ; then
		return 1
	fi

	# æ®‹ã‚Š
	left=$(echo -nE "$LBUFFER" | sed -e 's/[^[:space:]]*$//')
	LBUFFER=$left$abbrev
	return 0
}

# ãƒ‘ã‚¤ãƒ—ç•¥èªå±•é–‹
expand-pipe-abbrev()
{
	local left right abbrev
	# æœ€å¾Œã® | ä»¥é™ã‚’å–å¾—
	right=$(echo -nE "$LBUFFER" | sed -e 's/.*|\([^|]*\)$/\1/')
	abbrev=$pipe_abbrev[$right]
	
	if [ -z "$abbrev" ] ; then
		return 1
	fi

	# æ®‹ã‚Š
	left=$(echo -nE "$LBUFFER" | sed -e 's/[^|]*$//')
	LBUFFER=$left" "$abbrev" "
	return 0
}

# ç•¥èªå±•é–‹ || complete-word
expand-my-abbrev-or-complete()
{
	expand-pipe-abbrev || expand-word-abbrev || zle expand-or-complete
}

zle -N expand-my-abbrev-or-complete
bindkey "^I" expand-my-abbrev-or-complete

# For Emacs ansi-term
function set-eterm-dir() {
	echo 'AnSiTu' $(whoami)
	case "${OSTYPE}" in
		linux*)
			echo 'AnSiTh' $(hostname)
			;;
		cygwin*)
			echo 'AnSiTh' "GOGOTEA"
			;;
	esac
	echo 'AnSiTc' $(pwd)
	# for bash (share_history)
	# history -a
}
if [ $TERM = eterm-color ]; then
	# for bash
	# PROMPT_COMMAND=set-eterm-dir
	
	# for zsh
	if [ -n "$CYGWIN" ];then
		export PAGER=cat
	fi
	function chpwd() {
		set-eterm-dir
	}
fi

# mkdir and cd
function mkcd () {
	mkdir $1 && cd $1
}

case "${TERM}" in
screen*|ansi*)
	preexec() {
		# printf "\eP\e]0;${1%% *}\a\e\\"
		printf "\eP\e]0;${1}\a\e\\"
		#printf "\ek!$1\e\\"
	}
	precmd() {
		# printf "\eP\e]0;~$(basename $(pwd))\a\e\\"
		printf "\eP\e]0;~$(pwd)\a\e\\"
		#printf "\ek~$(basename $(pwd))\e\\"
	}
	;;
esac

